title: My life with my family
creator_credit: Negabanchi Tebeje, ACMI Digital Storytelling and ACMI
brief_description: Life, so far, has been quite a struggle for Negabanchi Tebeje and her family. With her dad fighting for democracy, the Tebeje family have moved from Ethiopia to Sudan and, finally, Australia.
